  "body": " Compute Logs Base 10   Load the question by clicking the button below.       Compute logs base 10    <p> Evaluate the following. <\/p> <ol class=\"HELM_parts_inline\"> <p><\/p><li>\\({@l1@} =\\) [[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]] [[feedback:prt1]]<\/li><p><\/p> <p><\/p><li>\\({@l2@} =\\) [[input:ans2]] [[validation:ans2]] [[feedback:prt2]]<\/li><p><\/p> <p><\/p><li>\\({@l3@} =\\) [[input:ans3]] [[validation:ans3]] [[feedback:prt3]]<\/li><p><\/p> <\/ol>    <p>Since \\(\\log_aA^k = k \\log_a A\\), we have <\/p><p>\\({@l1@} = \\log_{10} 10^{@aa@} = {@aa@}\\),<\/p> <p>\\({@l2@} = \\log_{10} 10^{@bb@} = {@bb@}\\),<\/p> <p>\\({@l3@} = \\displaystyle {@cc@}\\).<\/p>   1  0  0    2025073100    aa: rand(5)+1; bb: -rand(3)-1; cc: (rand(4)+1)\/5; aaa: 10^(aa); bbb: float(10^(bb)); l1: lg(aaa); l2: lg(bbb); l3: lg(10^(cc)); ta1: aa; ta2: bb; ta3: cc;       \\({@l1@} = {@aa@}, \\quad {@l2@} = {@bb@}, \\quad {@l3@} = {@cc@}\\)      1  0  0   <span style=\"font-size: 1.5em; color:green;\"><i class=\"fa fa-check\"><\/i><\/span> Correct answer, well done.    <span style=\"font-size: 1.5em; color:orange;\"><i class=\"fa fa-adjust\"><\/i><\/span> Your answer is partially correct.    <span style=\"font-size: 1.5em; color:red;\"><i class=\"fa fa-times\"><\/i><\/span> Incorrect answer.   .  *10  dot  1  i  cos-1  lang  [  0    ans1  algebraic  ta1  5  1  0   0  [[BASIC-ALGEBRA]],log,lg,ln   1  1  1  1  3     ans2  algebraic  ta2  5  1  0   0  [[BASIC-ALGEBRA]],log,lg,ln   1  1  1  1  3     ans3  algebraic  ta3  5  1  0   0  [[BASIC-ALGEBRA]],log,lg,ln   1  1  1  1  3     prt1  1.0000000  1  1      0   AlgEquiv  ans1  ta1   0  =  1   -1  prt1-1-T     =  0   -1  prt1-1-F        prt2  1.0000000  1  1      0   AlgEquiv  ans2  ta2   0  =  1   -1  prt2-1-T     =  0   -1  prt2-1-F        prt3  1.0000000  1  1      0   AlgEquiv  ans3  ta3   0  =  1   -1  prt3-1-T     =  0   -1  prt3-1-F       908439600  1036602090  1163022972  1265763752  532137283  372938422  580520982  230838769  204394558  1620987614   1    ans1  ta1    ans2  ta2    ans3  ta3    prt1  1.0000000  0.0000000  prt1-1-T    prt2  1.0000000  0.0000000  prt2-1-T    prt3  1.0000000  0.0000000  prt3-1-T     2    ans1  ta3    ans2  ta1    ans3  ta2    prt1  0.0000000  0.0000000  prt1-1-F    prt2  0.0000000  0.0000000  prt2-1-F    prt3  0.0000000  0.0000000  prt3-1-F       "
